<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en' style="height: 100%">
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
  <link rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.googleapis.com'/>
  <link rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.gstatic.com' crossorigin/>
  <link
    href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;500;800&display=swap'
    rel='stylesheet'
  />
  <title>Mimir: Don't forget to return the books!</title>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; height: 100%; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-style: normal;">
<table
  style="color: #333333; border-collapse: collapse; height: 100%; width: 100%; background-image: url('https://mimir-content.fra1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/background.png'); background-size: 2000px">
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2" height="75px"></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="height: 513px;">
    <td
      style="width: 408px; background-color: #fdfdfd; background-image: url('https://mimir-content.fra1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/MimirEmail.svg'); background-position: 100% 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; border-radius: 0 80px 80px 0; padding: 40px 85px 40px 40px;">
      <table style="border-collapse: collapse;">

        <tr>
          <td
            style="padding-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px;">
            Whoops! It looks like you forgot to return the book
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td
            style="padding-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-size: 15px; line-height: 18px;">
            A friendly reminder that you need to return the <q>{{bookName}}</q> book as soon as possible or extend the
            term of the borrowing
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td style="text-align: center;">
            <table style="border-collapse: collapse;">
              <tr>
                <td style="padding: 16px; background-color: #F4F6FA; border-radius: 10px;">
                  <table style="border-collapse: collapse;">
                    <tr>
                      <td>
                        <img src='{{bookCover}}' alt='book' style="max-width: 115px;"/>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td
                        style="padding-top: 8px; font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; word-break: break-word;">
                        {{bookName}}
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding-top: 16px;">
                  <a
                    style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; background: #1a1ed6; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 30px; height: 37px; color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; line-height: 37px; text-decoration: none;"
                    href='{{appUrl}}'>Go to app</a>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
    <td></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2" height="75px"></td>
  </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
